'''維珍尼亞·"吉妮"·卓華舒雅'''（{{lang-en|Virginia "Ginny" Thrasher}}<ref name="heavy">{{cite news | url=http://heavy.com/sports/2016/08/ginny-thrasher-west-virginia-who-won-the-first-gold-medal-team-usa-air-rifle-bio-wvu-rio-olympics/ | title=Ginny Thrasher: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know | work=heavy.com | date=2016-08-06 | accessdate=2016-08-07}}</ref>，{{bd|1997年|2月28日}}），美國女子氣步槍射擊選手<ref name="issf profile">{{cite web | url=http://www.issf-sports.org/athletes/athlete.ashx?personissfid=SHUSAW2802199701 | title=ISSF Athlete Profile | publisher=ISSF |accessdate=2016-10-18}}</ref>，代表美國參與10米氣步槍奧運決賽得分208.0環而奪得金牌<ref name="MyUser_Indianexpress.com_August_6_2016c">{{cite web |url=http://indianexpress.com/sports/rio-2016-olympics/live-day-1-schedule-scores-updates-medals-india-2957578/ |title=Rio 2016 Olympics, Day 1 Live blog: Virginia Thrasher of USA wins first gold medal |newspaper=Indianexpress.com |date=  |author= |accessdate= 2016-08-06}}</ref>，擊敗中國的[[杜麗|杜麗]]和[[易思玲|易思玲]]而成為2016年奧運首名奧運金牌得主<ref name="rio profile">{{cite web | url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/athlete/virginia-thrasher | title=Virginia Thrasher | publisher=Rio 2016 | accessdate=2016-08-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922155848/https://www.rio2016.com/en/athlete/virginia-thrasher | archive-date=2016-09-22}}</ref><ref name="first gold">{{cite web | url=https://sportscafe.in/articles/shooting/2016/aug/06/rio-2016-usa-s-virginia-thrasher-wins-first-gold-of-rio-olympics | title=Rio 2016 / USA's Virginia Thrasher wins first gold of Rio Olympics | publisher=sportscafe.in | accessdate=2019-10-28 | archive-date=2017-08-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823164754/https://sportscafe.in/articles/shooting/2016/aug/06/rio-2016-usa-s-virginia-thrasher-wins-first-gold-of-rio-olympics | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/rio-2016-olympics/news/shooting/Virginia-Thrasher-wins-first-gold-of-Rio-Olympics/articleshow/53574754.cms | title=Virginia Thrasher wins first gold of Rio Olympics | publisher=[[印度時報|印度時報]] | date=2016-08-06 | accessdate=2016-08-06 | archive-date=2016-08-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807112740/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/rio-2016-olympics/news/shooting/Virginia-Thrasher-wins-first-gold-of-Rio-Olympics/articleshow/53574754.cms | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

